title: Cyclone tipped to form on Sunday off Queensland's coast
description: The weather system is one of two tropical lows looming around Australia, creating strong winds along most of Queensland's coastline. Some modelling shows it moving as far south as the Wide Bay region.
content:
A tropical low off the Queensland coast has a high chance of becoming a cyclone as early as Sunday, with strong wind warnings in place for most of the state's coastline.
Bureau of Meteorology foreca… [+2535 chars]
de: Am Sonntag bildete sich vor der Küste von Queensland ein Zyklon. Das Wettersystem ist eines von zwei tropischen Tiefs, die rund um Australien drohen und starke Winde entlang des größten Teils der Küste Queenslands erzeugen. Einige Modellierungen zeigen, dass es sich bis in die Wide Bay-Region nach Süden bewegt.
en: Cyclone tipped to form on Sunday off Queensland's coast. The weather system is one of two tropical lows looming around Australia, creating strong winds along most of Queensland's coastline. Some modelling shows it moving as far south as the Wide Bay region.
